    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera represents a purist\u2019s entry into naturally aspirated flat-six performance. Powered by the 3.6L M96 engine featuring VarioCam Plus, the power delivery is linear and rewarding up to the 7,200 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers crisp engagement with short throws, paired with a rear-wheel-drive configuration for optimal steering feedback. Chassis dynamics are sharp, utilizing a front MacPherson strut and rear multi-link setup that communicates every nuance of the tarmac. This example has been properly maintained with the crucial IMS bearing and Rear Main Seal (RMS) upgrades already performed. While showing honest signs of use consistent with a well-driven sports car, the mechanical integrity remains high, providing a visceral, analog driving experience that modern, electronically-damped cars cannot replicate.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
