      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though there are minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful road use. The body panels are straight with excellent gap consistency and no signs of corrosion. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision. It features a fully documented service history, including a recent comprehensive inspection, oil change, and a fresh set of premium tires. This is a reliable, well-sorted example that perfectly balances performance with everyday practicality, ready for its next owner to drive with confidence.",
